Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,11點50分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個男人從後門進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿著許多貨物
