Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂～喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂～喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久城
